'''匹多莫德'''（{{lang-en|'''Pidotimod'''}}）是一种[[免疫增强剂|免疫增强剂]]类[[免疫调节剂|免疫调节剂]]，主要用于[[儿科|儿科]]，可以提高儿童[[免疫力|免疫力]]，预防或辅助治疗[[感染|感染]]性疾病。<ref name="pmid18806958">{{cite journal |author=Du XF, Jiang CZ, Wu CF, Won EK, Choung SY |title=Synergistic immunostimulating activity of pidotimod and red ginseng acidic polysaccharide against cyclophosphamide-induced immunosuppression |journal=Archives of pharmacal research |volume=31 |issue=9 |pages=1153–9 |date=September 2008 |pmid=18806958 |doi=10.1007/s12272-001-1282-6}}</ref>匹多莫德在[[中国|中国]]儿科使用非常广泛，常见商品名有'''芙露饮'''等。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.drugs.com/international/pidotimod.html | title=Pidotimod | accessdate=11 October 2015 | archive-date=2015-12-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222165754/http://www.drugs.com/international/pidotimod.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>匹多莫德面世至今已20多年，但仍缺乏高質量的臨床研究支持其功效，故有些醫生公開質疑處方本藥的療效和必要性<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2018-01-13/doc-ifyqqieu6135755.shtml |title=儿科常用药匹多莫德有效性遭质疑 缺乏大型临床数据 |accessdate=2018-01-13 |archive-date=2018-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113035806/http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2018-01-13/doc-ifyqqieu6135755.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
 
